1
00:00:01,700 --> 00:00:02,740
Hello, friend.

2
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:06,160
Hello, hello, buddy.

3
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:08,599
Şükran, you who understand polytheism, let me take a look.

4
00:00:08,980 --> 00:00:09,500
All right, sir.

5
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:11,740
What's up?

6
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:14,220
"No, we're not counting; not even a drop of water—we're not."

7
00:00:14,699 --> 00:00:16,000
There's a pair of pants there.

8
00:00:16,339 --> 00:00:17,820
The water is yours now—congratulations.

9
00:00:18,339 --> 00:00:21,100
We have nothing to do with the water; it’s because of my brother.

10
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,039
Do you mind?

11
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:23,920
So, do I belong here?

12
00:00:24,239 --> 00:00:24,899
The foreigner said.

13
00:00:25,899 --> 00:00:27,339
What a mess I’ve made.

14
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:28,739
You saw us in the garden.

15
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:30,140
Did you think there was a gardener?

16
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:31,960
I am Özgür, my driver.

17
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:33,600
Arif. Arif.

18
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:36,719
I’m also the world-class boxing champion, as you all know.

19
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:37,560
It's a mistake.

20
00:00:37,859 --> 00:00:38,060
He is.

21
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:39,979
That's when you get down to business.

